title: Zach Wilson and the Jets Stall Against the Patriots Once Again
description: Zach Wilson threw three puzzling interceptions and the Jets turned over an early lead to the Patriots. New England has won the past 13 regular-season meetings.
dc:creator: Jenny Vrentas
media:credit: Brad Penner/USA Today Sports, via Reuters
media:description: Jets quarterback Zach Wilson forced Devin McCourty out of bounds after the Patriots safety intercepted him for the second time on Sunday.
